                <p class="Body"><a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" title="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part1IntroductionToArm" href="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part1IntroductionToArm" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;">Day 2 Part 1</a> (49:02, 418 MB)<br></p>
                <p class="Body"><a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" title="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part2IntroductionToArm" href="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part2IntroductionToArm" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;">Day 2 Part 2</a> (15:23, 174 MB)<br></p>
                <p class="Body"><a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" title="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part3IntroductionToArm" href="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part3IntroductionToArm" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;">Day 2 Part 3</a> (26:36, 236 MB)<br></p>
                <p class="Body"><a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" title="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part4IntroductionToArm" href="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part4IntroductionToArm" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;">Day 2 Part 4</a> (37:21, 322 MB)<br></p>
                <p class="Body"><a onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" title="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part5IntroductionToArm" href="http://www.archive.org/details/Day2Part5IntroductionToArm" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;">Day 2 Part 5</a> (27:56, 237 MB)<br></p>
                <p class="Body">(6:12:26 total, sans lab time)<br></p>
                <p class="Body"><br></p>
                <p class="Body">The videos are useful for students, but also more useful for potential instructors who would like to teach this material. By watching the video, you will better understand the intent of some slides which do not stand on their own. You are recommended to watch the largest size video so that the most possible text is visible without having to follow along in the slides.<br></p>
